CNCP v1 23062
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7532: `:slotted` styles not being applied if slot is wrapped in `TransitionGroup`",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:09.342761+00:00",
  "text": "`:slotted` styles not being applied if slot is wrapped in `TransitionGroup`\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.2.45\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nWrap the slot contents in a `TransitionGroup`\n\n### What is expected?\n\nThe `:slotted` selector should style the contents of the `TransitionGroup`\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nStyles are not being applied to the contents of the `TransitionGroup`\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n`:deep` can be used instead and it doesn't have the same bug, but it may not be the perfect solution in all cases.",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: transition",
    "scope: slots",
    "has PR"
  ],
